{
  "stem": "15577.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I really went there, at least a few times a week.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- but it was only the first time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then they shortened it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At the end, only my father and some were left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, with time, nobody was left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was also a very, very special policy of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, they-- they throw out every Jewish family from-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from a house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It means-- these were all rented flats.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Almost 100% percent of the Jews were living in rented flats.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If the flat and-- or the house was a beautiful one, and a comfortable one, and well-equipped, and furnitured, so the chances were the-- I think it was, again, three, four months, maybe even earlier.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After the Germans came to Cracow, all these Jews were thrown out of their houses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Germans got them, because they-- as it was the capital, there were a lot of Germans, which came to Cracow, to live there as a governor employees, as-- as all possible thing.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they needed the-- the best way was to get the beautiful houses of the wealthy Jews, especially.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So a-- as I told you before, we were rather wealthy, and we had a very, very nice apartment.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- at that time, I didn't realize how nice it was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then I understood it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we were one of-- of the first who-- who-- where the Germans-- it was the whole house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the house of, if I'm not mistaken, 12 inhabitants, 12 flats were in there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean it's a whole-- it's a whole building.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The whole building, yeah, the whole building-- it was four floors, and very comfortable.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Germans came and threw out every Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
